Class SpaceCraft

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.Group
com.kihachu.spaceiteration1.model.SpaceCraft
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class SpaceCraft extends javafx.scene.Group
Represents a spacecraft in the universe. Provides functionality for moving, rotating, and mining resources from asteroids.
